lead_paragraph: Sunderland winger Adnan Januzaj has been ruled out for at least six weeks after sustaining an ankle injury in Saturday's Premier League defeat by Crystal Palace.

headline.print_headline: Sunderland's Januzaj Out For at Least Six Weeks
